WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.707
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.707 --> 00:00:02.834
Praise the Lord.

00:00:02.834 --> 00:00:04.960
Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:09.120
Well, it's Brandon and Diana again, and we have some things on our heart.

00:00:09.120 --> 00:00:13.876
You know, I've been asking the Lord, 'Lord, there's a lot going on right now.

00:00:13.876 --> 00:00:15.902
There is a lot going on.

00:00:15.902 --> 00:00:30.229
' I told you all we would start to see these things—what the spirit of the Lord was showing me in prayer: the earthquakes, the wars and rumors of wars, the escalation with Iran.

00:00:30.891 --> 00:00:37.439
It seems like all is being stirred up like a pot, isn't it?

00:00:37.439 --> 00:00:41.700
But you can feel there's something major about to take place.

00:00:41.960 --> 00:00:55.931
And then we have all the tariffs happening and all the things going on with that, and the economy crashing 1,500 points the day before and 2,000 today, and most people are like, 'What's going on?

00:00:55.931 --> 00:01:00.039
' You know, and everybody wants to—'Where'd you go, Braden?

00:01:00.039 --> 00:01:10.684
' Listen, if I don't feel the presence of the Lord on a video and I watch it back with my family and I just go, 'I'm not going to release it.

00:01:10.684 --> 00:01:18.180
' I vowed to the Lord: if I do not sense the presence of the Lord on a video, I'm doing my best.

00:01:18.180 --> 00:01:21.093
You know, some of them you may say, 'Well, I didn't feel nothing on that video.

00:01:21.093 --> 00:01:24.782
' Well, it was semi-okay, so I release it.

00:01:24.782 --> 00:01:31.220
But I'm telling you, if I feel a video is dry, I'm not going to waste your time.

00:01:31.220 --> 00:01:33.680
I just don't want to waste your time.

00:01:33.920 --> 00:01:40.079
I'd rather it just be nothing on the air at all than for me to come on here and just ramble around.

00:01:40.479 --> 00:01:45.600
If I feel a leading, I'm going to put it out, and this is one I feel a leading on.

00:01:45.600 --> 00:01:54.525
I was praying and I was asking the Lord about things, and He said, 'I want you to start reading the book of Jeremiah.

00:01:54.850 --> 00:02:06.331
I want you to go over Jeremiah and look at what he went through and the things that I called him to say and warn the people that were not ready to hear what he had to say.

00:02:06.331 --> 00:02:08.987
' They persecuted him for what was coming.

00:02:08.987 --> 00:02:16.720
They persecuted him because of the things that he was saying and decreeing by the voice of the Lord.

00:02:16.720 --> 00:02:19.320
He was saying, 'Hey, this judgment's coming.

00:02:19.320 --> 00:02:20.549
These things are coming.

00:02:20.549 --> 00:02:33.858
' And you have a lot of itching-ear people right now, a lot of prophetic voices like I told you all that are giving words at a level down here.

00:02:34.453 --> 00:02:44.599
I'm not here to criticize because I'm not going to point any names out; I'm just telling you what I've heard the spirit of the Lord say.

00:02:44.599 --> 00:03:03.188
They're so apt to want to be the first is what I'm hearing—to be the one that is always in the spotlight like a Hollywood celebrity wanting to have their name in lights instead of going higher.

00:03:03.188 --> 00:03:12.902
And the Lord told me, 'There's a lot of my ministers that are speaking from a level down here instead of looking out like an eagle.

00:03:12.902 --> 00:03:15.760
They're not looking at the eagle level.

00:03:15.760 --> 00:03:18.469
They're prophesying down here with the chickens.

00:03:18.469 --> 00:03:25.440
' And He said, 'And when you do that, you're only able to see the trees in front of your face.

00:03:25.440 --> 00:03:36.640
You cannot see from a far distance what's coming to warn the people because you're prophesying down where the chickens are.

00:03:36.640 --> 00:03:44.239
And if you don't get up where the eagles are because the eagle has an eagle-eyed view and they're able to see miles away.

00:03:44.239 --> 00:03:57.484
' An eagle is able to see miles; they're able to see a long way and they're able to tell what's coming in the future from storms or whatever because they're able to see it.

00:03:57.982 --> 00:04:01.360
But if they're down there with the chickens, you're only able to see the trees.

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:06.185
So, you're prophesying at the tree level and you need to come up higher in the mountain level.

00:04:06.185 --> 00:04:08.974
And that's where the Lord is.

00:04:08.974 --> 00:04:18.079
And the Lord told me, 'Brandon, are you not in the end times right now?

00:04:24.240 --> 00:04:24.400
' I said, 'Well, we see the signs, Lord.

00:04:24.400 --> 00:04:29.554
Of course I believe we're in the end times.

00:04:29.554 --> 00:04:38.827
' And He said, 'Then what did I say in my word was coming for those end-time people?

00:04:40.427 --> 00:04:49.260
If your generation is the closer generation—and we've heard it and heard it—if you are a closer generation, what are you expecting to come?

00:04:49.260 --> 00:04:54.524
' And He gave me Matthew 24.

00:04:54.524 --> 00:04:55.737
I want Diana to read this.

00:04:55.737 --> 00:04:58.068
And this is not a feel-good passage.

00:04:58.068 --> 00:05:01.069
This is not a feel-good, 'Wow, this makes me feel good.

00:05:01.069 --> 00:05:02.339
Oh, good times are coming.

00:05:02.339 --> 00:05:12.706
' If we're living in the last days, if we truly are living in the last days, what are we supposed to expect with an eagle-eyed view?

00:05:12.706 --> 00:05:14.780
What are we looking for?

00:05:15.070 --> 00:05:28.608
So, are we looking like everybody's saying there's good days coming, all this greatness is coming, 'Boy, I tell you what, this is going to be the best of the best'?

00:05:28.608 --> 00:05:31.199
Are we off when we say that?

00:05:39.100 --> 00:05:39.470
I don't know.

00:05:39.470 --> 00:05:40.420
Let's see.

00:05:40.420 --> 00:05:43.147
We're in the end times, right?

00:05:43.147 --> 00:05:46.320
So, what is the end?

00:05:46.320 --> 00:05:50.510
What did Jesus say we're supposed to expect?

00:05:50.510 --> 00:05:53.664
Go ahead and read chapter 24, verse 4.

00:05:56.400 --> 00:05:56.700
I want you to start there.

00:05:56.700 --> 00:06:03.320
Jesus answered them, 'Be careful that no one mislead you, deceiving you and leading you into error.

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:18.319
For many will come in on the strength of my name, appropriating the name which belongs to me, saying, "I am the Christ, the Messiah," and they will lead many astray.

00:06:22.253 --> 00:06:25.509
And you will hear of wars and rumors of wars.

00:06:25.509 --> 00:06:35.680
See that you are not frightened or troubled, for this must take place, but the end is not yet.

00:06:35.680 --> 00:06:43.120
For nation will rise against nation, and kingdom against kingdom, and there will be famines and earthquakes in place after place.

00:06:43.120 --> 00:06:44.046
' Pause.

00:06:44.046 --> 00:06:48.560
There'll be famines and there's going to be earthquakes in place after place.

00:06:48.560 --> 00:06:56.032
So, there's going to be earthquakes all over the place, major earthquakes.

00:06:56.032 --> 00:07:07.667
What I tell you is coming—the Lord said in 2025 we're going to start to see major earthquakes.

00:07:17.074 --> 00:07:17.486
Then we had the one in Asia.

00:07:17.486 --> 00:07:21.280
Then we had another one in Asia.

00:07:21.280 --> 00:07:22.469
There's more coming.

00:07:22.469 --> 00:07:23.360
Keep going.

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:26.582
There's pestilence and earthquakes, wars, rumors of wars.

00:07:26.582 --> 00:07:27.406
Keep going.

00:07:27.406 --> 00:07:34.000
'All this is the beginning, the early pains of the birth pains of intolerable anguish.

00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:42.591
They will hand you over to suffer affliction and tribulation and put you to death.

00:07:42.591 --> 00:07:48.800
And you will be hated by all nations for my name's sake.

00:07:48.800 --> 00:08:06.720
And then many will be offended and repelled and will begin to distrust and desert him whom they ought to trust and obey and will stumble and fall away and betray one another and pursue one another with hatred.

00:08:06.720 --> 00:08:14.993
And many false prophets will rise up and deceive and lead many into error.

00:08:27.590 --> 00:08:27.820
And the love of the great body of people will grow cold because of the multiplied lawlessness and iniquity.

00:08:27.820 --> 00:08:28.739
' Okay, pause.

00:08:34.098 --> 00:08:36.994
So, He's warning right there that there's going to be a lot of people fall away.

00:08:36.994 --> 00:08:46.200
There's going to be a lot of people that are going to be persecuted for His name's sake.

00:08:46.200 --> 00:08:53.160
You're going to be tested basically by the world persecuting you because you're a Christian.

00:08:53.160 --> 00:08:58.940
Then He said we're going to see lots of false prophets rise up.

00:09:02.250 --> 00:09:08.860
I don't know—like I've said this before—I don't know of any other denomination or belief system that has prophets other than the Christian community.

00:09:08.860 --> 00:09:10.229
We don't have Buddhist prophets.

00:09:10.229 --> 00:09:12.640
We don't have Muhammad prophets.

00:09:12.640 --> 00:09:23.369
I haven't heard any, but there's a lot of Christians and a lot of it is the charismatic circle.

00:09:37.680 --> 00:09:38.240
Many false prophets are going to rise up.

00:09:39.360 --> 00:09:43.744
So does that make these people bad?

00:09:43.744 --> 00:09:44.352
No.

00:09:58.320 --> 00:09:58.560
It just means they're not hearing Him.

00:09:58.560 --> 00:09:59.920
They're down with the chickens.

00:09:59.920 --> 00:10:01.680
They're not hearing a clear direction.

00:10:01.680 --> 00:10:08.630
So anybody who gives a word that is off, that automatically makes it false.

00:10:08.630 --> 00:10:12.080
But does that make them a bad person?

00:10:12.080 --> 00:10:12.674
No.

00:10:12.674 --> 00:10:14.622
Are they doing it out of malice?

00:10:14.622 --> 00:10:16.594
