00:10:16.594 --> 00:10:21.749
Are they saying, 'Well, we're going to lead all these people astray'?

00:10:21.749 --> 00:10:24.880
No, I believe they're just missing it.

00:10:24.880 --> 00:10:26.195
Many false prophets.

00:10:26.195 --> 00:10:28.479
It's not somebody that's out there.

00:10:28.906 --> 00:10:36.880
I don't believe there's a lot of these people, because I've talked to them, that are doing it and trying to be deceitful.

00:10:36.880 --> 00:10:48.576
They're just down with the chickens and they're listening in front of their face instead of coming up higher with the fire, getting at the throne room and sitting at his feet.

00:10:48.576 --> 00:10:56.556
