00:12:34.811 --> 00:12:39.005
When I hear sorrows, that seems sad.

00:12:39.005 --> 00:12:41.119
Sorrows is sad.

00:12:41.119 --> 00:12:44.204
That's a sad time.

00:13:00.747 --> 00:13:01.040
So it's the beginning of sorrows.

00:13:13.120 --> 00:13:27.851
So we have a lot of words being given, and I'm not here to point out people, but we have a lot of words being given about the United States is going to do all this stuff, and we're going to do all these things, and everything's going to get better for a season.

00:13:27.851 --> 00:13:41.424
And the Lord told me we have a window, a season of blessing for the remnant to get up the wealth of the wicked to lay up for the righteous.

00:13:44.639 --> 00:13:44.919
He said, 'Why?

00:13:44.919 --> 00:13:48.420
' Because there's great days of turbulence coming.

00:13:48.420 --> 00:13:50.898
Very hard days are coming.

00:13:50.898 --> 00:13:51.964
Matthew 24.

00:14:06.480 --> 00:14:06.800
So, let's keep reading.

00:14:06.800 --> 00:14:19.799
'But he who endures to the end will be saved, and this good news of the kingdom, the gospel, will be preached throughout the whole world as a testimony to all the nations.

00:14:29.047 --> 00:14:29.413
And then will come the end.

00:14:29.413 --> 00:14:38.297
